美化侵略戰爭和侵略行為，尋釁滋事，擾亂公共秩序，構成違反治安管理行為的，由公安機關依法給予治安管理處罰；構成犯罪的，依法追究刑事責任。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1bf8d7286622a50e433f0b3f10afb132e27798","tid":1101624,"uid":43808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"犯咗邊條法啊？法治喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3238d5f63db6056c7b67672834816519147b09ea","tid":1101624,"uid":10538,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"明明前排安倍去北京周街仲掛晒日本旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dde447f388b84c98b0177b839beb054e4547e73","tid":1101624,"uid":119008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7207481a6b1b5abcbea88c2792bbc24e8d97b664","tid":1101624,"uid":178337,"like":527,"dislike":3,"score":524,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"所以佢犯咩法? &quot;極大地傷害了廣大人民群眾的民族感情和愛國情懷&quot; 係一條法律?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"依家無 之後會有"},{"pid":"71da0f07c1251f557b0102e76b4fc2787120934b","tid":1101624,"uid":9951,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vfDZU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vfDZU.png&h=b7127dfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9055cc9616843689def8fbae0ae07eb09a673679","tid":1101624,"uid":33825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f7a9732a0e9bfc32ab956583b68d96ab70693d","tid":1101624,"uid":236682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T